Author: usr687
Text: I totally forgot to reply to your comment back to me on your last post, but I want to say again that you’re a great sibling. I’m glad things worked out! I was also glad to see you said you were seeing your own therapist before going out to see her. Taking care of yourself is also super important! I hope things are well for you both, stay safe❤️
